	<Title>
		Weight loss: Set yourself up for success
	</Title>
	<Body>
		&lt;p&gt;If you have a significant amount of weight to lose, it may be too discouraging to think about doing it all at once. Rather than focusing on a number, try focusing on making and sustaining healthy lifestyle changes. And aim for a realistic and attainable weight loss of 1 to 2 pounds (0.5 to 1 kilogram) a week.&lt;/p&gt;
